</P>
<P>
   REVIEW-FRIES _ Movie review. ``Home Fries.'' A smalltown
romantic comedy, scant on the romance, and too broad on the comedy.
</P>
<P>
   REVIEW-SPRINGER _ Movie review. ``Jerry Springer Ringmaster.''
OK, first, Angel beats the crap out of Willie. Then Starletta
smacks around Angel. There's a brief, non-punching interlude so
LeShawnette can scream at Demond and Angel can scream at Connie.
Then Angel attacks Demond, Starletta tries to tear out Angel's hair
and Angel returns to pounding on Willie.
</P>
<P>
   RELIGION
</P>
<P>
   INTERFAITH-MARRIAGES _ WEST PALM BEACH, Fla. _ Susann Ferarra
was not happy to learn that the rabbinical powers that be have
decreed her unfit to hold her job as executive director of Temple
Beth David in Palm Beach Gardens. She is, after all, a committed
Jew. She has dedicated her professional life to the Jewish
community and her personal life raising two observant children. But
she married a Catholic. And as far as the highest rabbinical
assembly in the Conservative movement is concerned, that means she
cannot be a positive role model. (Belkin, Palm Beach Post) MOVED.
</P>
