<P>
   UNDATED _ After the tumult of the past year, the retail industry
is fairly optimistic as they head into the important holiday
shopping season, which accounts for the bulk of many stores' sales
and profits. By KATHRYN HOPPER. Story will move in ``f'' financial
category. &QL; 
