the anniversary of the arrival of Spanish explorers in 1698, at the
presidio and village the Spanish created (now Pensacola Naval Air
Station). The historic area will be the setting for ceremonies
recognizing the area's oldest families as well as a parade and
fireworks. 1-800-874-1234.
