<HEADER>
A7261 &Cx1f; tab-z
r e &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-NYTBOOK-CONTENTS-UPDA     11-24 1101
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-NYTBOOK-CONTENTS-UPDATE-NYTSF </SLUG>
 
 (Adds cover story) 
 Editors: Following is a list of slugs and titles of the books
reviewed in the New York Times Book Review for Sunday Nov. 29.
<TEXT>
<P>
   ----------------------------------------------------
</P>
<P>
   ON THE COVER
</P>
<P>
   ----------------------------------------------------
</P>
<P>
   NYTBOOK-MATISSE-1000&AMP;ADD-NYTSF, THE UNKNOWN MATISSE, A Life of
Henri Matisse: The Early Years, 1869-1908. By Hilary Spurling.
Illustrated. 480 pp. New York: Alfred A. Knopf. $40 The first
volume of a biography of Matisse traces the struggles and
uncertainties of his early career.
</P>
<P>
