months of sitting on the sidelines. By Lynnley Browning. 500 words.
</P>
<P>
   AOL-NETSCAPE (Undated) -- AOL makes it official: It will
purchase Netscape for $4.2 billion, with a side deal with Sun
Microsystems. By Ross Kerber. 900 words.
</P>
