 &UR; ENTREPRENEUR PACKAGE &QL;  &LR; 
 &UR;  &QL;  &LR; 
 &UR; DESIGN  &LR; _ Berkeley architect Charles Debbas came up with the idea
for his finger-fitting Ergo pen after his hand cramped up sketching
for hours on end. Recent Stanford grad Chris Flink designed a
better shopping basket as part of a class assignment, and it could
soon make him a millionaire.
