<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-HEROIC-US-CONSUMERS-RESEND-NYTSF-WORTH </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
HOW LONG CAN U.S. CONSUMERS PROP UP WORLD ECONOMY?  
 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (Resending for those needing; moved 11-20)   (This excellent 1,000-word ``separate buy'' financial story is from
``WORTH'' magazine. To publish this article, it must be purchased
from New York Times sales representative NIRDI RELIS in New York at
1-800-972-3550 or 212-499-3333, or fax her at 212-499-3382.)  
  
 (PLEASE NOTE: This article has been filed into the ``f'' financial
news, ``a'' domestic/general and ``k'' commentary news files.)  
  
 By JIM JUBAK  
 c.1998 Worth Magazine  
 (Distributed by New York Times Special Features)  
<TEXT>
<P>
   The International Monetary Fund is out of dough. Politicians
