<HEADLINE>
FORGET JAPAN; LET'S FOCUS ON A RECESSION CLOSER TO HOME  
 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (Resending for those needing; moved 11-20)   (This insightful 1,000-word ``separate buy'' financial story is
from the November issue of ``WORTH'' magazine. To publish this
article, it must be purchased from New York Times sales
representative NIRDI RELIS in New York at 1-800-972-3550 or
212-499-3333, or fax her at 212-499-3382.)  
  
 (PLEASE NOTE: This article has been filed into the ``f'' financial
news, ``a'' domestic/general news and ``k'' commentary news
files.)  
  
