   &UR; (To publish this user-friendly ``WORTH'' magazine article, it
must be purchased from New York Times sales representative NIRDI
RELIS in New York at 1-800-972-3550 or 212-499-3333, or fax her at
212-499-3382.) &LR;  &QL;
</P>
