<SLUG> BC-HITLER-HOTEL-INDEPENDENT-NYTSF </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
HITLER'S ALPINE RETREAT TO BECOME LUXURY HOTEL COMPLEX  
 
</HEADLINE>
   (This 500-word ``separate buy'' article is from The Independent
newspaper in London.)  
  
 (To publish this article, it must be purchased from New York Times
Syndicate sales representative NIRDI RELIS in New York at
1-800-972-3550 or 212-499-3333, or fax her at 212-499-3382.)  
  
 (PLEASE NOTE: This article has been transmitted into the ``i''
international news, ``a'' domestic/general news and ``t'' travel
news files.)  
  
