<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-11-24 22:51 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A8091 &Cx1f; tab-z
r k &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-`BRAVE'-WORDS-ECONOMI     11-24 1139
